---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="About | GEN Engine Insights"
  description="About GEN Engine Insights - your guide to AI search engine optimization and generative engine optimization strategies."
>
  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">About GEN Engine Insights</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        GEN Engine Insights is dedicated to helping content creators, marketers, and business owners 
        navigate the rapidly evolving landscape of AI-powered search.
      </p>
      
      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>
        As AI search engines like ChatGPT, Perplexity, Google's SGE, and Claude increasingly become 
        the first point of discovery for information, traditional SEO strategies are no longer enough. 
        We bridge the gap between old-world SEO and the new era of Generative Engine Optimization (GEO).
      </p>
      
      <h2>What We Cover</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>GEO Strategies</strong> - How to optimize content for AI citation and discovery</li>
        <li><strong>AI Search Trends</strong> - Latest developments in AI-powered search engines</li>
        <li><strong>Zero-Click Optimization</strong> - Making your content the definitive answer</li>
        <li><strong>Crawler Optimization</strong> - Technical setup for AI web crawlers</li>
        <li><strong>Content Structure</strong> - Formatting content for AI comprehension</li>
        <li><strong>Authority Building</strong> - Establishing expertise that AI engines trust</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2>Why GEO Matters</h2>
      <p>
        The shift from traditional search to AI-generated answers is happening faster than most 
        realize. When someone asks ChatGPT or Perplexity a question, the AI cites sources it 
        considers authoritative and well-structured. GEO is about becoming one of those sources.
      </p>
      
      <blockquote>
        "The best time to optimize for AI search was yesterday. The second best time is now."
      </blockquote>
      
      <h2>Get Started</h2>
      <p>
        Explore our <a href="/blog">blog</a> for actionable insights and strategies. 
        Whether you're just starting out or looking to deepen your GEO expertise, 
        we have content for every level.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
